# Git & PR workflow

Aries is a fork of [JesusChapman/valentine](https://github.com/JesusChapman/valentine). This repository is **HighScientist22/aries**.

## Remotes & PR targets

- **Only push and open PRs against this repo** (`origin` → `HighScientist22/aries`).
- **Never** open pull requests to `JesusChapman/valentine` or any other upstream Valentine repo.
- **Do not** add an `upstream` remote to Valentine unless the user explicitly asks for read-only syncing.
- When using `gh pr create`, ensure the head/base repos are `HighScientist22/aries` branches — not the fork parent.

## Commits

- Follow existing commit message style on the current branch.
- Exclude `xcuserdata/`, `.DS_Store`, `Aries.dmg`, and `Secrets.swift` unless the user explicitly requests them.
